    "The identified topics ranged from specific drug therapies (e.g., proteasome inhibitors, CAR T-cell therapy) to disease mechanisms (e.g., bone remodeling, imaging techniques) and clinical aspects (e.g., graft-versus-host disease, transplantation).",
    "These topics provide a high-level overview of the main research themes in multiple myeloma and can serve as a foundation for organizing the chatbot's knowledge base and generating informative responses.",
